(7, 'IPL Auction To Be Held Overseas For The First Time,Dubai Confirmed As Venue', 3, 4, '<p>NEW DELHI: In first,the Indian Premier League auction this year will be held overseas as Dubai on Friday was finalised by BCCI as the venue for the event.</p><p><br></p><p>The IPL Auction will be held on December 19 at the Coca-Cola Area in the desert city ,according to media report.</p><p><br></p><p>In a communicationto all the 10 franchises,the BCCI also informed the deadline for the release of the list of retained player been xtended to November 26.The earluer date to submit the list of retained players was November 15.</p><p><br></p><p>Rs 100 crore each has also been decided as the salary cap of 10 franchises.<br></p>', '2023-11-03 18:30:00', '2023-11-04 11:51:44', 1, 'IPL-Auction-To-Be-Held-Overseas-For-The-First-Time,Dubai-Confirmed-As-Venue', 'fee1c617249e53317e3a199f8694fde6.jpg', 25, 'admin', 'admin'),
